Anywhere  where you want in that file 

Right so now go to [font=arial][size=14pt]Client.java[/size][/font]

add add this [code]public String loginMsgs() {
		int loginMsgs = Misc.random(4);
		switch(loginMsgs) {
			case 0: return "+ Config.WELCOME_MESSAGE +";
			case 1: return "+ Config.WELCOME_MESSAGE2 +";
			case 2: return "+ Config.WELCOME_MESSAGE3 +";
			case 3: return "+ Config.WELCOME_MESSAGE4 +";
		}
	}
[/code] Where ever you want 

Lastly go and look for you welcome message and replace it whith [code]sendMessage(loginMsgs());[/code]

